WEBVTT

1
01:24:04.430 --> 01:24:06.690 
他们还年轻  不是吗
They're young, aren't they?

2
01:24:12.210 --> 01:24:15.230 
我以为年岁的增长
One thing I assume of age

3
01:24:15.950 --> 01:24:17.370 
会导致厌倦
is weariness.

4
01:24:18.120 --> 01:24:20.800 
真希望我不会每天感到更加厌倦
Damned if I don't get more tired every day.

5
01:24:21.490 --> 01:24:23.210 
厌倦于我的工作
Tired of what I do.

6
01:24:23.720 --> 01:24:26.510 
沿着蛛丝马迹
Following arcs like lobbed rocks,

7
01:24:26.760 --> 01:24:28.810 
直至那不可避免的真相
the inevitability of truth.

8
01:24:32.000 --> 01:24:33.820 
但是问题的复杂性和灰色地带
But the complexity and the gray

